ike":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T09:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/25/175145_841624ffd316e0d71ce0d16a4b9a9338.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F25%2F175145_841624ffd316e0d71ce0d16a4b9a9338.jpg&h=9c79fc7e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab256e5af1fb4de40c8ed0204429061912d08e1","tid":435763,"uid":44093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T11:28:40.000Z","msg":"片尾曲係咩名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b4849603edb49ef172076c7e40b774b42a8575","tid":435763,"uid":102689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>片尾曲係咩名？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHold The Light by Dierks Bentley"},{"pid":"db9075c01421aa8780cd72e04abe0d09a8bd302c","tid":435763,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T12:34:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>成套戲架機都累事 又飛落消防員人羣到 又淋錯水<br />\n又收唔到指示</blockquote><br />\n連續三次 淋錯條防火線真係好戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n最大敵人唔係大自然<br />\n係飛機個D豬隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45740fe7a68eb5943ab02cf53e88212cdf9596fe","tid":435763,"uid":30215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T15:27:52.000Z","msg":"好彩趕喺雷神上畫前睇左<br />\n好戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大美國得嚟唔誇張<br />\n又唔會刻意煽情<br />\n描寫情緒點到即止<br />\n結果估到，但真係好無常"},{"pid":"90e1c94aa119d1367993de27bf211e28c2f61d2a","tid":435763,"uid":106621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T16:45:28.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post 岩岩去左睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0d5ba8caa325e03f5c1213b248b4c7bd02a60b5","tid":435763,"uid":65372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:59:10.000Z","msg":"好好睇<br />\n最尾知道成隊死晒然後崩潰果度真係好撚sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb82be74c0f74845e532cb7352bfcbf30dc56b1","tid":435763,"uid":154684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:30:28.000Z","msg":"miles teller啲戲好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91862d3afc4c4449754141fe9b7d4e24afcff50a","tid":435763,"uid":86360,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>外國既山火真係勁多同規模大好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔好以將外國乜撚野都攞黎比啦唔該你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港樓宇又細密度又高, 咁既環境下救火救人, 消防員自己都好危險, 難度係世界級<br />\n<br />\n外國山火首先好少要救人, 已經無得比. 山火講緊係如何strategically控制蔓延程度, 點似香港消防員攞命駁?</blockquote><br />\n正解<br />\n<br />\n好多國際排名入面 香港消防員都排頭幾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n外國消防員一年死亡數一定多過香港 <br />\n<br />\n無錯香港密度高又成，但香港防火系統已經好好<br />\n而且外國今時今日好多屋用木做 ，一燒上黎就唔停<br />\n<br />\n你話山火由佢燒 控制下程度，你睇番外國紀錄片，山火最危險，十秒間個火已經由好遠山頭燒到埋身，決定慢左就死係山上 無人會救你</blockquote><br />\n係咪戇撚鳩架 咁都有得鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n鬥贏左 威威d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啲弱智咩都要踩下自己人先開心 <br />\n總之香港嘅就咩都差過人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n外國就算係屎都係香嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2710476334181806b0ac52f0aa81183444312178","tid":435763,"uid":32516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T15:07:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>miles teller啲戲好掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nwhiplash<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a358b791d2eb45add53a982329d55c44479523e8","tid":435763,"uid":63732,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:16:33.000Z","msg":"女朋友睇到喊"},{"pid":"7473b5fa25231f4cc862c0c16ff2bc7d51b6bb1a","tid":435763,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實塊野係咪真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲火成千度喎 我覺得就咁訓係塊野下面 點都變燒豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n所以最後咪證明左比你睇有無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n投咗水嘅話唔知有冇得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3b24e377977ff29b4453598c6cb1693bda12444","tid":435763,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最尾首歌 好撚好聽</blockquote><br />\n有幾個得21歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多2字頭"},{"pid":"90ba26ea181a4c6083dc2e337fe08e4c6976742b","tid":435763,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-27T15:20:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇到喊撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺棵樹下面影嗰張相好正<br />\n男人的浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇到現實嗰班真係有影<br />\n即刻成個後腦麻痺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\